column5: How was the West arm nippising fishing last weekend? Heading there this weekend myself. Just want pike action and a couple walleye to eat. Any tips would be greatly appreciated. Thanks
your answers lye in the post of the lakeair G2G. read it and weep!!!!!!
Nipissing was real tough last week, but the weather was mainly to blame for that. It will only get better in the next couple weeks.
